    <item>
      <title>伦敦金属交易所计划采取措施促进月度合约交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金属交易所（London Metal Exchange）正计划采取措施，促进其月度合约的电子交易，此举可能会减少其独特的三个月滚动合约的活动，该合约是全球金属行业的基准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/lme-planning-measures-to-boost-trading-in-monthly-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司获英国批准建造耗资 24 亿英镑的巨型水库</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/thames-water-gets-uk-approval-for-giant-2-4-billion-reservoir</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国批准泰晤士水务有限公司在牛津郡建造一座备受争议的价值 24 亿英镑的水库的计划，以帮助避免未来几十年伦敦和英格兰东南部出现干旱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/thames-water-gets-uk-approval-for-giant-2-4-billion-reservoir</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:02:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
